metadata.name: BAFC #1
metadata.description: The Bored Ape Football Club is an NFT based on all the football players from countries participating in the World Cup championship in Qatar. The players are all ready to participate, but due to genetic engineering that occurs during the registration of the fingerprint process, all of these soccer players have turned into ancient monkey DNA and must compete for medicine to turn them back into humans. Can you help them get their medicine?
